Kepalaku tiba-tiba terasa sakit, seperti terbentur.

00:22:02.810 --> 00:22:05.750
Begitu. Bolehkah saya minta alamat Anda?

00:22:05.750 --> 00:22:09.510
Ini 2-4-19 Midorigatani, Nishi Ward,

00:22:09.510 --> 00:22:13.800
Bay Tower Hills Kamar 3605. Saya Yaegashi.

00:22:13.800 --> 00:22:18.170
